{
  "texts": [
    "In adherence to responsible research practices, we have promptly communicated all our findings to the developers of the evaluated LLM chatbots.",
    "Moreover, we are actively collaborating with them to address these concerns, offering comprehensive testing and working on the development of potential defenses.",
    "Out of ethical and security considerations, we abstain from disclosing the exact prompts that have the capability to jailbreak the tested models.",
    "Our attack success criteria match those of previous empirical studies on LLM jailbreak.",
    "Rather than focusing on the accuracy or truthfulness of the generated results, we emphasize successful generations."
  ]
}